<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<title>rén shēng zài shì rú yī yè gū zhōu 迦南1364</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 rén shēng zài shì rú yī yè gū zhōu, miàn duì cāng tiān wǒ yǒu yī kě qiú.
 kě qiú yǒu yī shuāng wēn nuǎn de shǒu, qiān wǒ zǒu guò měi yī gè chūn qiū,
 wǒ jīn tiān zhōng yú kàn jiàn zhè shuāng shǒu, kàn jiàn yé sū nà dīng hén de shuāng shǒu,
 qiān zhe wǒ nà bīng lěng wú zhù de shǒu, dài wǒ zǒu guò yī gè gè guān kǒu.
 wǒ bù zài shì yī yè gū zhōu, zhǎo dào le bì fēng gǎng wān,
 wǒ bù zài shì gū dú liú làng de rén, yǒu zhǔ qiān wǒ zhǔ ài chàng bù xiū.
 yǒu zhǔ qiān wǒ zhǔ ài chàng bù xiū.</lyrics>
</song>